20
00:01:41,310 --> 00:01:43,440
I was a disciple expelled
by Big Medicine Valley.

21
00:01:43,950 --> 00:01:45,680
Master thought

22
00:01:45,680 --> 00:01:47,360
I was good at poison,

23
00:01:47,360 --> 00:01:49,120
not medicine.

24
00:01:49,400 --> 00:01:51,230
I was too evil

25
00:01:51,440 --> 00:01:52,630
to have Book of Almighty Medicine

26
00:01:52,630 --> 00:01:55,360
and be the head of the Valley.

27
00:01:55,360 --> 00:01:57,480
I got in a rage and defected.

28
00:01:58,000 --> 00:01:59,590
It’s you who took me in.

29
00:01:59,830 --> 00:02:01,000
Yeah.

30
