38
00:02:19,800 --> 00:02:22,110
Things have changed.

39
00:02:22,110 --> 00:02:24,470
I’m no longer the chief of Anping Army.

40
00:02:24,470 --> 00:02:26,960
We haven’t got

41
00:02:26,960 --> 00:02:28,800
the Color of Ocean and Heaven.

42
