Tong Tianyang. Chu Tianyu. Lu Tiankuang.

45
00:02:45,800 --> 00:02:47,830
They were all defeated by some kids

46
00:02:47,830 --> 00:02:50,390
with Fortress of the Forty-Eight.

47
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:52,470
Tianying.

48
00:02:52,470 --> 00:02:54,360
They don’t even know

49
00:02:54,360 --> 00:02:56,030
what the Color of Ocean and Heaven

50
00:02:56,030 --> 00:02:57,440
is.

51
00:02:57,440 --> 00:02:58,470
Their victory

52
00:02:58,470 --> 00:03:00,550
is nothing but fluke.

53
00:03:00,720 --> 00:03:02,270
Sooner or later,

54
00:03:02,270 --> 00:03:04,470
I will get back

55
