56
00:03:08,080 --> 00:03:09,470
What’s your plan?

57
00:03:09,470 --> 00:03:11,720
Zhou Fei has got Fire Lotus.

58
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:12,910
Her next target

59
00:03:12,910 --> 00:03:14,720
should be the Flaming Sage

60
00:03:14,720 --> 00:03:16,080
at Cloud Ravine in the south,

61
00:03:16,080 --> 00:03:18,360
to resist the poison
in Xiao Chuan’s system.

62
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:20,750
I’m going to kill her

63
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,700
and get back the Seal of Cautiousness.

64
00:03:27,520 --> 00:03:29,620
May you come back soon.

65
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:33,270
Don’t go astray.

66
00:03:36,020 --> 00:03:37,470
(Demons Manor)

67
00:03:37,470 --> 00:03:40,160
I was an orphan in the snow mountain,

68
00:03:40,160 --> 00:03:43,110
living with beasts and
suffering from hunger.

69
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:45,750
You saved me

70
00:03:45,750 --> 00:03:47,440
and gave me a new life.

71
00:03:48,470 --> 00:03:50,160
I only

72
00:03:50,720 --> 00:03:52,630
trust you.

73
00:03:53,240 --> 00:03:54,720
I have

74
00:03:54,720 --> 00:03:55,670
a task for you.

75
00:03:56,720 --> 00:03:59,750
Badly, I was still late.

76
00:04:00,160 --> 00:04:01,910
Liu Youliang who escorted the map

77
00:04:01,910 --> 00:04:05,910
failed to keep the secret.

78
00:04:07,080 --> 00:04:09,240
I had a deal with Phoenix Master.

79
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,880
He helped me get Fire Lotus.

80
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:12,030
I must

81
00:04:12,030 --> 00:04:14,360
give him the Seal of Cautiousness.

82
00:04:14,830 --> 00:04:17,350
They are all after
the Color of Ocean and Heaven.

83
