What is it exactly?

84
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:20,880
Master.

85
00:04:20,880 --> 00:04:22,390
Do you know it?

86
00:04:22,830 --> 00:04:24,160
Well...

87
00:04:24,550 --> 00:04:28,070
Anzhi is supposed to tell you.

88
00:04:28,070 --> 00:04:30,440
If you are eager to know,

89
00:04:30,440 --> 00:04:32,270
go ask your father,

90
00:04:32,270 --> 00:04:33,790
Lord Gantang.

91
00:04:33,790 --> 00:04:35,440
My father?

92
00:04:37,550 --> 00:04:39,720
Go to see him

93
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:43,320
and he’ll tell you everything.

94
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:47,600
Why don’t you see Anzhi before leaving?

95
00:04:48,720 --> 00:04:50,070
I...

96
00:04:50,670 --> 00:04:52,110
I won’t.

97
00:04:58,390 --> 00:05:00,320
I’m afraid I can’t leave

98
00:05:00,640 --> 00:05:02,480
if I see him.

99
00:05:10,790 --> 00:05:12,070
Lord Gantang.

100
00:05:13,640 --> 00:05:14,950
Thanks.

101
00:05:33,480 --> 00:05:36,040
Is it from Madam Li?

102
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:38,200
Can you tell by a touch?

103
00:05:46,640 --> 00:05:48,510
I know from this.

104
00:05:56,830 --> 00:05:58,550
Sir. A girl is asking to see you.

105
00:05:58,550 --> 00:05:59,440
She gave me this.

106
00:05:59,440 --> 00:06:01,000
Guards thought it was a prank.

107
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:02,920
So, they didn’t dare to disturb you.

108
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:03,670
I’ve checked it.

109
00:06:03,670 --> 00:06:06,000
I think you may have a look.

110
00:06:18,510 --> 00:06:19,790
Who is so bold?

111
00:06:19,790 --> 00:06:20,950
It’s fine.

112
00:06:21,350 --> 00:06:22,510
Let her in.

113
00:06:22,510 --> 00:06:23,320
Yes.

114
00:06:25,230 --> 00:06:27,550
Alright. You’re free to go.

115
00:06:28,230 --> 00:06:29,270
Yes.

116
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:48,270
Lord Gantang is in the camp ahead.

117
00:06:57,640 --> 00:06:58,880
Please.

118
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:05,160
He’s inside.

119
00:07:17,790 --> 00:07:18,660
Fei.

120
00:07:19,440 --> 00:07:20,270
Father.

121
00:07:32,230 --> 00:07:33,830
Fei.

122
00:07:33,830 --> 00:07:35,920
You look taller, don’t you?

123
00:07:36,790 --> 00:07:39,760
Father, it’s been a while.

124
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:44,070
Fei.

125
00:07:44,670 --> 00:07:46,950
I didn’t take you with me when I left.

126
00:07:47,350 --> 00:07:49,000
Do you blame me now?

127
00:07:52,350 --> 00:07:53,670
I know.

128
00:07:54,830 --> 00:07:57,320
My girl is tough.

129
00:07:58,070 --> 00:07:59,160
Tell me.

130
00:07:59,160 --> 00:08:01,670
Where have you been all this time?

131
00:08:02,920 --> 00:08:05,070
Well... A long story.

132
00:08:05,070 --> 00:08:06,760
Let’s talk inside.

133
00:08:09,270 --> 00:08:10,270
Are you all right?

134
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,720
I’m fine.

135
00:08:13,720 --> 00:08:16,550
It’s been windy.

136
00:08:17,440 --> 00:08:18,670
You look thin.

137
00:08:20,110 --> 00:08:21,760
It’s understandable.

138
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:24,880
In the Fortress,

139
00:08:25,510 --> 00:08:27,000
your mother used to

140
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,510
go hunting and pick flesh vegetables

141
00:08:28,510 --> 00:08:30,110
for me.

142
00:08:30,110 --> 00:08:31,600
But I got nothing here.

143
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:39,080
You still wear this old gown she made?

144
00:08:39,080 --> 00:08:41,230
It’s not old.

145
00:08:41,230 --> 00:08:43,550
The clothes she made are
the best to keep warm.

146
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:57,150
Is this

147
00:08:57,150 --> 00:08:58,960
the highly praised Anping Army?

148
00:09:00,590 --> 00:09:04,350
In troubled times, there must be someone
standing out.

149
00:09:06,320 --> 00:09:08,760
Suddenly, I can understand him,

150
00:09:08,760 --> 00:09:10,400
and my mother,

151
00:09:10,910 --> 00:09:12,640
and Xie Yun.

152
00:09:22,320 --> 00:09:25,200
Come. I have a gift for you.

153
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,230
Father.

154
00:09:26,230 --> 00:09:27,880
Is it a welcome gift?

155
00:09:27,880 --> 00:09:29,200
You’re humorous.

156
00:09:46,710 --> 00:09:47,880
Take a look.

157
00:09:58,260 --> 00:09:59,780
(Unbreakable)

158
00:10:01,470 --> 00:10:05,030
It’s named Unbreakable.

159
00:10:17,200 --> 00:10:19,200
Is it some poison?

160
00:10:20,400 --> 00:10:24,280
Top poisons are colorless and tasteless.

161
00:10:24,280 --> 00:10:26,320
I’m telling you out of kindness.

162
00:10:26,790 --> 00:10:28,150
Try it.

163
00:10:28,550 --> 00:10:30,280
No.

164
00:10:30,280 --> 00:10:31,670
I won’t.

165
00:10:31,670 --> 00:10:34,030
Why don’t you try it?

166
00:10:34,030 --> 00:10:35,320
If I try,

167
00:10:35,320 --> 00:10:36,840
who will record

168
00:10:36,840 --> 00:10:38,470
the symptoms and reactions?

169
00:10:38,470 --> 00:10:40,400
Look. I’ve made the antidote for you.

170
00:10:40,400 --> 00:10:41,320
What do you fear of?

171
00:10:41,320 --> 00:10:43,470
Your last poison got me in bed for days.

172
00:10:43,470 --> 00:10:45,080
I won’t do it again.

173
00:10:45,080 --> 00:10:47,960
You asked me to study Bone-chilling.

174
00:10:47,960 --> 00:10:49,960
Is it Bone-chilling?

175
00:10:51,470 --> 00:10:53,880
Bone-chilling is extremely complicated
to prepare.

176
00:10:53,880 --> 00:10:55,400
The formula is long gone.

177
00:10:55,400 --> 00:10:56,230
The toxicity of this poison

178
00:10:56,230 --> 00:10:58,960
is not even one tenth of Bone-chilling.

179
00:10:58,960 --> 00:11:01,350
Drink it and have the antidote at once.

180
00:11:01,350 --> 00:11:03,200
Nothing will happen.

181
00:11:03,550 --> 00:11:05,520
Why don’t you get Li Yan to try it?

182
00:11:05,520 --> 00:11:07,200
Are you talking about me?

183
00:11:08,350 --> 00:11:10,030
-No, nothing.
-No, nothing.

184
00:11:10,030 --> 00:11:12,320
We... We have new clothes for you.

185
00:11:12,320 --> 00:11:14,200
You said you’d buy new clothes.

186
00:11:14,200 --> 00:11:16,230
So, he wants you to try them.

187
00:11:17,840 --> 00:11:19,880
That doesn’t matter.

188
00:11:19,880 --> 00:11:22,030
Look, a letter from Fei.

189
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:23,550
She is safe and sound.

190
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:25,080
Isn’t Xie Yun dead?

191
00:11:25,080 --> 00:11:26,350
Fei also said

192
00:11:26,350 --> 00:11:28,550
Xie’s master had got the formula.

193
00:11:28,550 --> 00:11:29,200
Fei is

194
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:31,590
looking for the ingredients.

195
00:11:31,590 --> 00:11:32,840
