196
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:36,440
Fire Lotus. Flaming Sage.

197
00:11:36,440 --> 00:11:37,840
Flaming Sage?

198
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:40,200
The name rings a bell.

199
00:11:42,200 --> 00:11:45,230
It only grows in Cloud Ravine.

200
00:11:45,230 --> 00:11:47,880
Sir, have you ever heard of it?

201
00:11:48,110 --> 00:11:49,030
You bonehead.

202
00:11:49,030 --> 00:11:51,280
Why did they get you as the leader?

203
00:11:51,640 --> 00:11:53,110
What else did she say?

204
00:11:53,110 --> 00:11:54,590
Would she go to Cloud Ravine?

205
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:58,760
Father, don’t worry about me.

206
00:11:58,760 --> 00:12:00,150
Ordinary martial artists

207
00:12:00,150 --> 00:12:01,520
are no match to me.

208
00:12:01,520 --> 00:12:03,520
I’ve also fought Demons more than once.

209
00:12:05,150 --> 00:12:06,760
It’s so kind of you, Father.

210
00:12:06,760 --> 00:12:09,200
You know I need a blade.

211
00:12:12,230 --> 00:12:13,640
Actually,

212
00:12:13,640 --> 00:12:16,790
I’ve been looking for a good blade
for you.

213
00:12:17,760 --> 00:12:20,110
The world has been in chaos.

214
00:12:20,110 --> 00:12:21,840
Good blades are

215
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,350
getting less.

216
00:12:24,080 --> 00:12:28,230
I also had men find ancient blades,

217
00:12:28,230 --> 00:12:31,400
yet few of them fit you.

218
00:12:32,000 --> 00:12:34,110
Some of the ancient blades

219
00:12:34,110 --> 00:12:35,880
are mediocre in quality.

220
00:12:35,880 --> 00:12:37,150
Some of them are

221
00:12:37,150 --> 00:12:39,550
subject to ominous tales.

222
00:12:40,230 --> 00:12:42,440
Finally, I got this blade.

223
00:12:42,960 --> 00:12:44,790
It’s perfect for you.

224
00:12:46,150 --> 00:12:47,840
Lyu Run,

225
00:12:47,840 --> 00:12:49,760
